v1.0.	8th December 2011

First version with autoconf/automake build system

v1.1.	Quite a while after that.

Support for the newer API from artifastring and more
command line options.

v1.2.	5th Nov 2015

MIDI modulation wheel can now set replace the pedal
in an emergency (--pedal=modwheel); New ModulationEventListener
class permits Pedals to be informed of MIDI CC1 events;
various up-tidying. NJB/.
